Preburn fuel loading noted below is therefore much less than would have resulted from logging before a fire. Piles are concentrated mainly along one major road through the project area along a drainage bottom. Elevation is average elevation of the entire project area; piles exist both above and below the given elevation.

Piles are concentrated mainly along one major road through the project area along a drainage bottom. Elevation is average elevation of the entire project area; piles exist both above and below the given elevation.
